Whitelist Campaign ROUND.2

Dec. 22, 2021（ Dec. 29, 2021 addition）

About the First Whitelist Campaign

The first Whitelist campaign ended on December 19, 2021, and thanks to all of you, the total number of registered users in each community has grown to over 85K !

I would like to take this opportunity to express my deepest gratitude to all of you.

About the Whitelist Campaign Round.2

Thanks to the support of our community, it has been decided that GensoKishi Online -META WORLD- will be supported by TrustPad and will also have a launch on their platform.

To express our deepest gratitude, we have decided to hold a second Whitelist campaign, where 100 winners will be selected by lottery to win a total of $10,000 worth of MV tokens!

How to earn entry points

As with the previous Whitelist campaign, we are looking forward to further strengthening our community with your help.

・Enter the campaign.
・Obtain invitees via the campaign’s referral URL
・Follow the Twitter account
・RT of fixed tweets on Twitter
・Joining a Discord server
・Joining a Telegram group

Again, these are the ways to earn entry points.
The more entry points you have, the more likely you are to be selected in the lottery, so make sure you earn as many points as possible to be eligible for the exclusive MV token sale!

How to participate in the campaign

↓ ↓ ↓ ↓ ↓ ↓ ↓ ↓ ↓
Whitelist Campaign
Click here to access

Please enter your name and email address in the login section in the middle of the page and select “Enter Giveaway”.

This completes your entry into the campaign.

※Note
・If another person has already entered with the same IP address, you may not be able to enter. (This may be resolved by disconnecting the wifi connection.)
・If the problem persists, changing your browser may solve the problem.

About the campaign period

Starts：December 22, 2021
Ends：January 13, 2022

Please note that after the campaign is over, we will send the winning notification to the winner’s email address.

Please make sure that you can receive e-mails from info@genso.game.

Restricted countries: United States, China, Hong Kong, and all authorized OFAC countries (DR Congo, Iran, Myanmar, Sudan, Iraq, Cote d’Ivoire, North Korea, Syria, Zimbabwe, Cuba, Belarus, Liberia)
